hello welcome to devops world
    scm --->> source code management
           git --->>is central repository tool
	         --> both modes cli&gui
		 --> more secure & logs for every event
		 -->> installation is very fast & easy..


		 git logs
		      -->> git log
		           git log -n
			   git log --oneline
			   git log --since=yy-mm-dd
			   git log --since="yy-mm-dd hh:mm"
			      (or)
			   git log --after="yy-mm-dd hh:mm"
			   git log --author=name of the author
			   git log --grep="label id"
			   git log --filename

			   git log --until=yy-mm-dd
			        (or)
	                   git log --before="yy-mm-dd hh:mm"
			   git clone path/of/c-repository
			   git push
			   git reset HEAD filename
			   git reset --soft cid
			   git reset --mixed cid
			   git reset --hard cid (delete)
			   git show
			   git status
			   git init
			   git config --list
			   git config --global user.name=name 
